Class DirectionChangeEvent

java.lang.Object
java.util.EventObject

nz.ac.wgtn.swen225.lc.domain.state.DirectionChangeEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class DirectionChangeEvent extends PropertyChangeEvent
Represents an event containing a change in player position and an associated change in their direction. This event is used to pass data from the controller to the renderer containing the change of direction.
